tures\n\n1. Immersive VR Experience\n\n    Dive into the neon-drenched streets of Neo-Shinobi with stunning VR visuals. The high-fidelity graphics and realistic soundscapes create an unparalleled sense of immersion, making you feel as if you are truly in the midst of a cyberpunk dystopia.", "short_description": "Storyline\n\nIn the heart of a neon-lit metropolis, where the lines between the ancient and the futuristic blur, chaos reigns. The city of Neo-Shinobi is under siege by powerful criminal syndicates and rogue AI. As the last surviving member of an ancient ninja clan, you are thrust into a battle for survival and justice. Armed with a katana and a high-tech gun, your mission in \"Blade and Bullet\" is to defend the city from relentless assaults and restore peace to Neo-Shinobi.\nKey Features\n"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/blade-and-bullet/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "BROWN1451 Invention", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/blade-and-bullet", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1592192974313489"}, {"id": "1436351953220286"}, {"id": "459781504968480"}], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED_FOR_SOME_CONTENT", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "26123991423880865"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1637575616785367"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1637575616785367"}, "is_approved": tru